name: majicMIX reverie
description:
A 2.5D model I merged based on majicMIX_lux. It has a similar approach as majicMIX_fantasy but is not directly related, so I named it "reverie". You may figure it out through my examples.

试试这两个插件 I used mcmonkeyprojects/sd-dynamic-thresholding: Dynamic Thresholding (CFG Scale Fix) for SD Auto WebUI (github.com)

AND Bing-su/adetailer: Auto detecting, masking and inpainting with detection model. (github.com)

works extremely well with zhongfenghua style which is definitely undervalued
